    {
      "id": "74670c11-02b2-4eab-938b-d4ffa033b537",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The transition back to face to fface learning may have hindered the ability of some students to learn. After all, COVID demanded a substantial change to one’s study habits and it may have been hard for some students to go back to the previous normal. Therefore, it is important to understand what potential risk factors exist for low performance. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "74670c11-02b2-4eab-938b-d4ffa033b537",
        "parent": {
