    {
      "id": "98315ce3-885a-4a2a-8dce-7de13bd57e0f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Standard ML models often find it hard to identify insights that may be useful for the design of early interventions. To address this, the authors create a Random Forest trained under 3 distinct pruning paradigms:",
